_🧹 Nitpick_ | _🔵 Trivial_ | _⚡ Quick win_

**Drive the VHI-4 branch tests from `WALL_SPLAT_SPEED`, not fixed velocities.**

These tests currently bake in the present threshold with `6.0` and `3.0`. A legitimate retune of `WALL_SPLAT_SPEED` can flip the intended branch coverage here even when the production logic stays correct.

<details>
<summary>♻️ Suggested change</summary>

